               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184603300007"></xptr>
               <p>Odell's compliments, they were short of cash, and he would be glad if I would discount a 65<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. bill for him, and that I would take up the 30<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., one—this was on the 9th of March, the day it was due—I said, "Certainly," and in the afternoon he brought me this bill, accepted by Odell, for 65<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., at two months date, payable at the same place—I gave him a check for the whole amount, told him to go to my bankers, Robarts and Co., and take up the bill—he received the check, but did not take the bill up—he begged hard the bill might not be presented, as they should not like it to be returned</p>
